    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Install/upgrade-individual-nodes.dita" xtrc="p:1;6:8">Whether you are performing an online or
      offline upgrade, the steps for upgrading an individual nodes in a cluster remain the
      same.</p>
    
    <ol class="- topic/ol " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Install/upgrade-individual-nodes.dita" xtrc="ol:1;10:9">
