        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Install/upgrade-individual-nodes.dita" xtrc="li:2;12:13">Backup data for that node. To backup an existing Couchbase Server installation, use
