            using cbbackup</xref>.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Install/upgrade-individual-nodes.dita" xtrc="li:3;16:13">Backup the node-specific configuration files. While the upgrade script perform a
          backup of the configuration and data files, as a best practice, make your own
          backup of these files.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Install/upgrade-individual-nodes.dita" xtrc="li:4;19:13">Stop Couchbase Server.</li>
